'''第一号热带低气压'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Depression One}}）是[[1988年大西洋飓风季|1988年大西洋飓风季]]形成的第一个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，也是1963年的[[飓风弗洛拉|飓风弗洛拉]]过后在[[古巴|古巴]]产生降水最多的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，直到[[2005年大西洋飓风季|2005年]]才被[[飓风丹尼斯|飓风丹尼斯]]超越。系统于5月30日经[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]西北部的[[热带扰动|扰动天气]]发展而成，然后向东北方向移动，未经增强就在[[古巴|古巴]][[哈瓦那省|哈瓦那省]][[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。低气压的组织结构在穿越该国期间变得非常混乱，进入[[佛罗里达海峡|佛罗里达海峡]]后于6月2日退化成开放式[[低压槽|低压槽]]。虽然强度只达到热带低气压标准，但气旋却在古巴中部和西部产生超过1000毫米雨量，造成37人死亡，上千幢房屋受损，另有约6万5000人撤离。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|1-L 1988 track.png}}
5月31日，第一号热带低气压在西[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]经[[热带扰动|扰动天气]]发展形成<ref name="CLIQR">{{cite web | author = David M. Roth | year = 2011 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/roth/ebtrk_nhc_final.txt | title = Extended Best Track Database for CLIQR program | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2016-06-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304002251/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/roth/ebtrk_nhc_final.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>，比[[1988年大西洋飓风季|这年大西洋飓风季]]正式开始还要早一天<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | date = 1988-06-01 | newspaper = The Deseret News | title = Storm signals the arrival of hurricane season | accessdate = 2016-06-07 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=6T5TAAAAIBAJ&sjid=VIQDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6999,19361&dq=hurricane&hl=en | archive-date = 2021-05-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210529124832/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=6T5TAAAAIBAJ&sjid=VIQDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6999%2C19361&dq=hurricane&hl=en }}</ref>。气旋朝东北方向移动，在[[青年岛|青年岛]]西北方向近海掠过后从[[哈瓦那|哈瓦那]]以南袭击[[古巴|古巴]]本土。穿越该国期间，系统产生的大部分降水主要集中在中心以东，其风速始终未能超过每小时45公里。<ref name="CLIQR" /><ref name="rain">{{cite web | author = David M. Roth | date = 2008-08-04 | title = Tropical Depression #1 - May 30-June 2, 1988 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160527072645/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain//td1of1988.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-05-27 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2016-06-07 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain//td1of1988.html }}</ref>[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]也预计，气旋在[[风切变|风切变]]的影响下不大可能再出现进一步强化<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | date = 1988-06-01 | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | newspaper = Boca Raton News | title = Tropical depression born on schedule | accessdate = 2016-06-07 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=5x1UAAAAIBAJ&sjid=MI0DAAAAIBAJ&pg=6664,12725&dq=tropical+cuba&hl=en | archive-date = 2022-04-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220412013812/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=5x1UAAAAIBAJ&sjid=MI0DAAAAIBAJ&pg=6664%2C12725&dq=tropical+cuba&hl=en }}</ref>。6月2日，[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机已无法在系统中定位环流<ref name="ap0601am">{{cite news | title = Forecasters Watching Depression | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = Domestic News | agency = Associated Press | date = 1988-06-01}}</ref>，气象机构因此预计低气压已在[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]以东洋面退化成开放式[[低压槽|低压槽]]<ref name="CLIQR"/><ref name="rain" />。

== 影响及善后 ==
[[File:Tropical_Depression_One_1988_rainfall.gif|thumb]]的降水分布]]
第一号热带低气压在穿越古巴期间降下暴雨，该国[[西恩富戈斯省|西恩富戈斯省]]、[[比亚克拉拉省|比亚克拉拉省]]、[[圣斯皮里图斯省|圣斯皮里图斯省]]、[[卡马圭省|卡马圭省]]和[[谢戈德阿维拉省|谢戈德阿维拉省]]受到影响。全国以西恩富戈斯省降雨量最高，达到1025毫米，其中有867毫米是在一天内降下，第一号热带代气压由此成为有纪录以来在古巴产生降水第二多的热带气旋，仅次于1963年的飓风弗洛拉，直至[[2005年大西洋飓风季|2005年]]才被飓风丹尼斯超越。<ref name="CUBARAIN">{{cite web | author = Instituto Nacional de Recursos Hidráulicos | year = 2003 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131105222344/http://www.hidro.cu/hidrologia1.htm | title = Lluvias intensas observadas y grandes inundaciones reportadas | accessdate = 2013-11-05 | url = http://www.hidro.cu/hidrologia1.htm | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2013-11-05 }}</ref>此外，[[西恩富戈斯|西恩富戈斯]]和[[圣斯皮里图斯市|圣斯皮里图斯市]]的降雨量也分别达到578毫米和556毫米<ref name="rw">{{cite web | author = [[联合国人道事务协调厅|United Nations Department of Humanitarian Affairs (DHA)]] | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 1988-06-10 | title = Cuba - Heavy Rains Jun 1988 UNDRO Information Report No. 1 | accessdate = 2016-06-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304204846/http://reliefweb.int/report/cuba/cuba-heavy-rains-jun-1988-undro-information-report-no-1 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/cuba/cuba-heavy-rains-jun-1988-undro-information-report-no-1 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。

暴雨在[[卡马圭|卡马圭]]引发洪灾，导致约5700套房屋受损，200套被毁<ref name="rw" /><ref name="ria0608">{{cite news | title = Cuba -- Flood | publisher = The Russian Information Agency | date = 1988-06-08}}</ref>。洪灾还致使共计15所学校和医院受损，另有多幢农业建筑受到破坏<ref name="rw" />。受洪水影响，古巴有大面积地区的供电和通讯中断，该国中部和西部有六座桥梁被毁，另有多条公路和铁道受损，交通基础设施受到重创<ref name="ap0602am" />。全国共有131条道路因洪水导致无法通行，还有55条铁道受到破坏<ref name="rw" />。面对洪灾威胁，政府官员将生活在低洼地区的约6万5000居民撤离<ref name="ap0602am" />，在此期间还曾动用直升机和两栖交通工具<ref name="timesdaily">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | date = 1988-06-03 | title = Depression downgraded | accessdate = 2016-06-07 | via = Google news | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=joQ0AAAAIBAJ&sjid=nMgEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3527,336217&dq=tropical+cuba&hl=en | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = Times Daily | archive-date = 2022-04-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220412013809/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=joQ0AAAAIBAJ&sjid=nMgEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3527%2C336217&dq=tropical+cuba&hl=en }}</ref>。卡马圭市内出现[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，致使五架[[苏联|苏联]]飞机和多幢建筑毁于一旦<ref name="ap0602am">{{cite news | title = Storm Kills 14, Six Missing in Cuba | via = Google news | newspaper = International News | author = Staff Writer | agency = Associated Press | date = 1988-06-02 | accessdate = 2016-06-07 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=cElOAAAAIBAJ&sjid=KBQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=2928,1017398&dq=tropical+cuba&hl=en | archive-date = 2022-04-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220412013809/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=cElOAAAAIBAJ&sjid=KBQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=2928%2C1017398&dq=tropical+cuba&hl=en }}</ref>。截至气旋消散次日，古巴政府已确认九人丧生<ref name="timesdaily" />，最终确定的遇难人数达到37<ref name="CUBARAIN" />，此外低气压还导致数以千计的牲畜死亡<ref name="rw" />。洪灾过后，[[国际红十字与红新月运动|红十字会]]向古巴灾民提供援助，通过飞机向灾区运送医疗队、帐篷、毛毯及其它必要物资<ref name="ria0608rlf">{{cite news | title = Relief Aid to Cuba | publisher = The Russian Information Agency | date = 1988-06-08}}</ref>，该国共有约九万人受到这场风暴影响<ref name="rw" />。

第一号热带低气压产生的大部分降水都位于中心以东，所以在佛罗里达州产生的雨量不大。[[迈阿密|迈阿密]]地区降雨量约在25毫米左右，该州以[[庞帕诺比奇_(佛罗里达州)|庞帕诺比奇]]降水最多，达到81毫米。<ref name="rain" />

